XML:

{code}
<?xml version='1.0'?>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/404040404.dtd">
<html/>
{code}

Code:

{code}
scala.xml.XML.loadFile(new java.io.File("1.xml"))
{code}

fails:

